<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> <span lang="fr" xml:lang="fr"><i>Travail sur l'Algérie</i></span>, <span lang="la" xml:lang="la"><i>op.cit.</i></span> p. 752 (quoted in <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(English)</span> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFOlivier_LeCour_Grandmaison2001">Olivier LeCour Grandmaison (June 2001). <a href="http://mondediplo.com/2001/06/11torture2" class="external text" title="http://mondediplo.com/2001/06/11torture2" rel="nofollow">"Torture in Algeria: Past Acts That Haunt France — Liberty, Equality and Colony"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Le_Monde_diplomatique" title="Le Monde diplomatique">Le Monde diplomatique</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://mondediplo.com/2001/06/11torture2" class="external free" title="http://mondediplo.com/2001/06/11torture2" rel="nofollow">http://mondediplo.com/2001/06/11torture2</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Torture+in+Algeria%3A+Past+Acts+That+Haunt+France+%26mdash%3B+Liberty%2C+Equality+and+Colony&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Olivier+LeCour+Grandmaison&amp;rft.au=Olivier+LeCour+Grandmaison&amp;rft.date=June+2001&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BLe+Monde+diplomatique%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmondediplo.com%2F2001%2F06%2F11torture2&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Alexis_de_Tocqueville"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>)</li>
<li id="cite_note-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16" title="">^</a></b> Tocqueville, <span lang="fr" xml:lang="fr">Oeuvres completes</span>, III, 1, Gallimard, 1962, pp.299–300).</li>
<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> Tocqueville, <span lang="fr" xml:lang="fr">Oeuvres completes</span>, III, 1, Gallimard, 1962, pp. 303.</li>
<li id="cite_note-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18" title="">^</a></b> Tocqueville, <span lang="fr" xml:lang="fr">Œuvres complètes</span>, III, 1, Gallimard, 1962, pp. 299–306.</li>
<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.revue-lebanquet.com/fr/art/2001/299.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.revue-lebanquet.com/fr/art/2001/299.htm" rel="nofollow">Arguments in favor of Tocqueville</a>, Jean-Louis Benoît <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(French)</span></li>
</ol>
</div>
